install global https://www.npmjs.com/package/autocannon
for example rut test: autocannon -c 1000 -d 60 http://localhost:3000/ ---- where
-c is count opened conections
-d is timer(sec)
autocannon you need install better in global(-g) environment 
****************************************************************
if you'll use one thread, then run server.js
if you'll use multi threading, then run cluster.js
if you need stop some kind thread enter next commands: KILL <pid>, TASKKILL /F /PID <pid>(for the Windows OS)